{"storyMeta":{"storyReviewType":"NONE","storyId":"main_6_level_main_06-04_end","storyGroup":"main_6","storySort":8,"storyDependence":"main_6_level_main_06-04_beg","storyCanShow":0,"storyCode":"6-4","storyName":"溃烂的疮疤","storyPic":null,"storyInfo":"某个破旧的房间，一名整合运动成员在和一名女性对话。\n他们从历史聊到今天，最后，整合运动成员向女性提出一同离开龙门的邀请。\n","storyCanEnter":1,"storyTxt":"obt/main/level_main_06-04_end","avgTag":"行动后","unLockType":"STAGE_CLEAR","costItemType":"NONE","costItemId":null,"costItemCount":0,"stageCount":1,"requiredStages":[{"stageId":"main_06-04","minState":"PASS","maxState":"COMPLETE"}],"prev":6,"next":8,"characters":["整合运动成员","？？？"]},"lines":[{"type":"HEADER","key":"title_test","skippable":"true","mode":"BLACK_MASK","text":"第四关（后）","id":0},{"type":"Background","screenadapt":"coverall","image":"bg_indoor_n","width":"1","height":"1","fadetime":"2","block":"true","id":1},{"type":"Delay","time":"1","id":2},{"type":"PlayMusic","intro":"$darkness02_loop","key":"$darkness02_loop","volume":"0.8","crossfade":"1.5","delay":"0.5","id":3,"musicid":0},{"type":"Character","name":"char_1002_nsabr_1","id":4},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"整合运动成员","text":"外面已经乱作一团了。","id":5,"figure":"char_1002_nsabr_1"},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"整合运动成员","text":"听说梅菲斯特用法术变出了会袭击自己人的怪物，那些东西连感染者都吃。","id":6,"figure":"char_1002_nsabr_1"},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"整合运动成员","text":"哈，这场仗我们已经彻底打输了。","id":7,"figure":"char_1002_nsabr_1"},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"整合运动成员","text":"梅菲斯特留下的一支小队，刚才才有人在贫民区一间房的地下室里找到他们。","id":8,"figure":"char_1002_nsabr_1"},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"整合运动成员","text":"据说尸体上长满了植物，已经快认不出来了。你有头绪吗？","id":9,"figure":"char_1002_nsabr_1"},{"type":"Dialog","id":10},{"type":"Character","id":11},{"type":"Character","name":"avg_npc_043_1","fadetime":"1","block":"true","id":12},{"type":"Delay","time":"1","id":13},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"？？？","text":"不太清楚。","id":14,"figure":"avg_npc_043_1"},{"type":"Character","name":"char_1002_nsabr_1","name2":"avg_npc_043_1","focus":"1","id":15},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"整合运动成员","text":"真奇怪啊，怎么四处都是怪事。","id":16,"figure":"char_1002_nsabr_1"},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"整合运动成员","text":"切尔诺伯格打得下来，却攻不破龙门，果然还是因为塔露拉没来吧。","id":17,"figure":"char_1002_nsabr_1"},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"整合运动成员","text":"不和弑君者他们一起走好像也是选对了，通讯频道里已经完全搜不到他们的消息了。","id":18,"figure":"char_1002_nsabr_1"},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"整合运动成员","text":"这里就只剩我们这么点人，似乎也做不成什么事，哎。","id":19,"figure":"char_1002_nsabr_1"},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"整合运动成员","text":"你呢，你怎么说，龙门的感染者？","id":20,"figure":"char_1002_nsabr_1"},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"整合运动成员","text":"哎，龙门人。其实不加入整合运动，你可能也不至于变得和我们一样惨。","id":21,"figure":"char_1002_nsabr_1"},{"type":"Character","name":"char_1002_nsabr_1","name2":"avg_npc_043_1","focus":"2","id":22},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"？？？","text":"不加入，我们的处境也不会变好。","id":23,"figure":"avg_npc_043_1"},{"type":"Character","name":"char_1002_nsabr_1","name2":"avg_npc_043_1","focus":"1","id":24},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"整合运动成员","text":"......你是不是听了塔露拉的演讲才加入的？","id":25,"figure":"char_1002_nsabr_1"},{"type":"Character","name":"char_1002_nsabr_1","name2":"avg_npc_043_1","focus":"2","id":26},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"？？？","text":"不，口号对我没有吸引力。","id":27,"figure":"avg_npc_043_1"},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"？？？","text":"你会这么问我......似乎你也对感染者的身份政治不感兴趣。","id":28,"figure":"avg_npc_043_1"},{"type":"Character","name":"char_1002_nsabr_1","name2":"avg_npc_043_1","focus":"1","id":29},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"整合运动成员","text":"哦，看来你确实不信那套。","id":30,"figure":"char_1002_nsabr_1"},{"type":"Character","name":"char_1002_nsabr_1","name2":"avg_npc_043_1","focus":"2","id":31},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"？？？","text":"那为什么你还留在整合运动？","id":32,"figure":"avg_npc_043_1"},{"type":"Character","name":"char_1002_nsabr_1","name2":"avg_npc_043_1","focus":"1","id":33},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"整合运动成员","text":"因为除了整合运动，我也没其它地方能去啊。不过，是不是我们不来，你们就还能正常过活？","id":34,"figure":"char_1002_nsabr_1"},{"type":"Character","name":"char_1002_nsabr_1","name2":"avg_npc_043_1","focus":"2","id":35},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"？？？","text":"对感染者的清洗总会发生，整合运动只是会加速龙门的这个过程。","id":36,"figure":"avg_npc_043_1"},{"type":"Character","name":"char_1002_nsabr_1","name2":"avg_npc_043_1","focus":"1","id":37},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"整合运动成员","text":"你看得还挺清楚的。","id":38,"figure":"char_1002_nsabr_1"},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"整合运动成员","text":"也是。你说的没错。我的故乡，一座挺偏远的小城市，原本对感染者还算不错。","id":39,"figure":"char_1002_nsabr_1"},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"整合运动成员","text":"统治我们的贵族有个感染者女儿，在他的自治领里面，我们感染者能在隔离区里正常生活，矿役也不算特别重。","id":40,"figure":"char_1002_nsabr_1"},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"整合运动成员","text":"非患者对我们也没多好，但至少也会和我们进行交易，做点小买卖什么的，偶尔还能蹲在墙边一起喝点酒。","id":41,"figure":"char_1002_nsabr_1"},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"整合运动成员","text":"过了几年以后，好像是因为带兵打输了，伯爵被带走，新的市长上任了。","id":42,"figure":"char_1002_nsabr_1"},{"type":"Character","name":"char_1002_nsabr_1","name2":"avg_npc_043_1","focus":"2","id":43},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"？？？","text":"“大叛乱”？","id":44,"figure":"avg_npc_043_1"},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"？？？","text":"如果是那段时间，被削爵是很正常的事情。","id":45,"figure":"avg_npc_043_1"},{"type":"Character","name":"char_1002_nsabr_1","name2":"avg_npc_043_1","focus":"1","id":46},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"整合运动成员","text":"可能是吧，政治之类我不懂，都是后来有一句没一句的听来的。","id":47,"figure":"char_1002_nsabr_1"},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"整合运动成员","text":"他们说有的地方有感染者信使，但乌萨斯肯定没有，我们什么事都不知道。","id":48,"figure":"char_1002_nsabr_1"},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"整合运动成员","text":"起初大家还像以前一样过着日子，只是偶尔觉得氛围很沉重，食品供应商那的进货也越来越少。","id":49,"figure":"char_1002_nsabr_1"},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"整合运动成员","text":"慢慢地，气氛不大对了。物资短缺的时候，非患者开始向我们丢石头，身边也不断有感染者失踪。","id":50,"figure":"char_1002_nsabr_1"},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"整合运动成员","text":"十几场市政厅演说过后，已经没人提他贪污拨款和私自改造下城区的事了。","id":51,"figure":"char_1002_nsabr_1"},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"整合运动成员","text":"哼，这事我们感染者都知道，普通市民真能一点都不知道？","id":52,"figure":"char_1002_nsabr_1"},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"整合运动成员","text":"在隔离墙的边上，我们也能听见“除掉感染者，净化城市”之类的口号了。向隔离区里面这么喊的。","id":53,"figure":"char_1002_nsabr_1"},{"type":"Character","name":"char_1002_nsabr_1","name2":"avg_npc_043_1","focus":"2","id":54},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"？？？","text":"你们成了他私欲的牺牲品。","id":55,"figure":"avg_npc_043_1"},{"type":"Character","name":"char_1002_nsabr_1","name2":"avg_npc_043_1","focus":"1","id":56},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"整合运动成员","text":"物尽其用嘛，反正我们不一直都是牺牲品吗？就算我说之前我们城待感染者不错，其实也就好过那么几十年而已。","id":57,"figure":"char_1002_nsabr_1"},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"整合运动成员","text":"后面的事就很简单了，大多数感染者都被杀了。我们逃到荒野里，没吃没喝，又死了一大半。","id":58,"figure":"char_1002_nsabr_1"},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"整合运动成员","text":"这回在龙门，再死了一批。我的同乡已经死完了。","id":59,"figure":"char_1002_nsabr_1"},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"整合运动成员","text":"所以你说的对。这种事总会发生，感染者就是没地方能活。之所以还抱侥幸心理，都是因为事情没发生在眼前。","id":60,"figure":"char_1002_nsabr_1"},{"type":"Character","name":"char_1002_nsabr_1","name2":"avg_npc_043_1","focus":"2","id":61},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"？？？","text":"你和我说这些做什么？","id":62,"figure":"avg_npc_043_1"},{"type":"Character","name":"char_1002_nsabr_1","name2":"avg_npc_043_1","focus":"1","id":63},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"整合运动成员","text":"觉得自己没多少时间可活了啊。你会不会那种无痛的杀人方法？","id":64,"figure":"char_1002_nsabr_1"},{"type":"Character","name":"char_1002_nsabr_1","name2":"avg_npc_043_1","focus":"2","id":65},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"？？？","text":"......你在说什么？","id":66,"figure":"avg_npc_043_1"},{"type":"Character","name":"char_1002_nsabr_1","name2":"avg_npc_043_1","focus":"1","id":67},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"整合运动成员","text":"嗯？","id":68,"figure":"char_1002_nsabr_1"},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"整合运动成员","text":"啊......","id":69,"figure":"char_1002_nsabr_1"},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"整合运动成员","text":"对不起？我可能会错意了。","id":70,"figure":"char_1002_nsabr_1"},{"type":"Character","name":"char_1002_nsabr_1","name2":"avg_npc_043_1","focus":"2","id":71},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"？？？","text":"龙门人依然会痛恨你们，你们入侵了我们的城邦。","id":72,"figure":"avg_npc_043_1"},{"type":"Character","name":"char_1002_nsabr_1","name2":"avg_npc_043_1","focus":"1","id":73},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"整合运动成员","text":"是啊。可感染者哪有城邦呢？","id":74,"figure":"char_1002_nsabr_1"},{"type":"Character","name":"char_1002_nsabr_1","name2":"avg_npc_043_1","focus":"2","id":75},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"？？？","text":"......","id":76,"figure":"avg_npc_043_1"},{"type":"Character","name":"char_1002_nsabr_1","name2":"avg_npc_043_1","focus":"1","id":77},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"整合运动成员","text":"咦？起火了？","id":78,"figure":"char_1002_nsabr_1"},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"整合运动成员","text":"哎，别扯我......你说一声，我会给你让开窗户前的位置啊，用不着那么暴力吧。","id":79,"figure":"char_1002_nsabr_1"},{"type":"Character","name":"char_1002_nsabr_1","name2":"avg_npc_043_1","focus":"2","id":80},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"？？？","text":"火势蔓延得很迅速。奇怪，这不像是自然滋生的火灾。","id":81,"figure":"avg_npc_043_1"},{"type":"Character","name":"char_1002_nsabr_1","name2":"avg_npc_043_1","focus":"1","id":82},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"整合运动成员","text":"为啥？","id":83,"figure":"char_1002_nsabr_1"},{"type":"Character","name":"char_1002_nsabr_1","name2":"avg_npc_043_1","focus":"2","id":84},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"？？？","text":"它没有像“真正的火”那样蔓延。","id":85,"figure":"avg_npc_043_1"},{"type":"Character","name":"char_1002_nsabr_1","name2":"avg_npc_043_1","focus":"1","id":86},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"整合运动成员","text":"那我们赶紧撤离吧，谁知道接下来这里会变成什么样。","id":87,"figure":"char_1002_nsabr_1"},{"type":"Character","name":"char_1002_nsabr_1","name2":"avg_npc_043_1","focus":"2","id":88},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"？？？","text":"去哪里？","id":89,"figure":"avg_npc_043_1"},{"type":"Character","name":"char_1002_nsabr_1","name2":"avg_npc_043_1","focus":"1","id":90},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"整合运动成员","text":"看情况。那个，你要不要和我们走？你们龙门人离开故乡也有点难受吧。但你可以和我们一起离开。","id":91,"figure":"char_1002_nsabr_1"},{"type":"Character","name":"char_1002_nsabr_1","name2":"avg_npc_043_1","focus":"2","id":92},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"？？？","text":"我要不要和你们走？","id":93,"figure":"avg_npc_043_1"},{"type":"Character","name":"char_1002_nsabr_1","name2":"avg_npc_043_1","focus":"1","id":94},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"整合运动成员","text":"对啊。没事，我就问问，不愿意就算了。","id":95,"figure":"char_1002_nsabr_1"},{"type":"Character","name":"avg_npc_043_1","id":96},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"？？？","text":"......我考虑一下。","id":97,"figure":"avg_npc_043_1"},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"？？？","text":"不过，故乡......","id":98,"figure":"avg_npc_043_1"},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"？？？","text":"哪里才是故乡？","id":99,"figure":"avg_npc_043_1"},{"type":"delay","time":"0.6","id":100},{"type":"Dialog","id":101},{"type":"Blocker","fadetime":"2","block":"true","id":102},{"type":"Image","id":103}],"characters":["整合运动成员","？？？"]}